metadata.name: TiME-mACHINE
metadata.description:
The artwork tells the story of how the time machine was created to help the two individuals travel through time and explore different historical moments. The AI uses its intelligence to calculate the best route and prevent any alterations in the timeline.

The image shows the two individuals interacting with the AI to set the travel route, excited for what's to come. The artwork represents the collaboration between artificial intelligence and humans, and how together they can achieve things that once seemed impossible.
